 * - Get FPDF http://fpdf.org/
 * - Get OCRB font http://sprain.ch/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/OCRB_FPDFConverted.zip
 * - Move OCRB font files into the font folder of the FPDF class
 * - See example.php and get started
